              "text": "When the monster Strikes a creature that has the flat-footed condition with an agile or finesse melee weapon, an agile or finesse unarmed attack, or a ranged weapon attack, it also deals the listed precision damage. For a ranged attack with a thrown weapon, that weapon must also be an agile or finesse weapon.",
              "type": "ability"
            }
          },
          "name": "Sneak Attack",
          "offensive_action_type": "ability",
          "subtype": "offensive_action",
          "type": "stat_block_section"
        },
        {
          "ability": {
            "ability_type": "offensive",
            "action_type": {
              "name": "Two Actions",
              "subtype": "action_type",
              "type": "stat_block_section"
            },
            "critical_failure": "The creature takes double damage, becomes frightened 3, and is fleeing until the end of its next turn.",
            "critical_success": "The creature is unaffected and is temporarily immune for 1 minute. ",
